@startuml Place Lifecycle State Machine
title Place / Accommodation Lifecycle

[*] --> Draft

Draft --> PendingModeration: User submits for review
Draft --> Draft: Edit (allowed during draft)

PendingModeration --> Approved: Admin/moderator approves
PendingModeration --> Rejected: Admin/moderator rejects
PendingModeration --> Draft: Rejected → user can re-edit

Approved --> Published: Admin publishes or auto-publish
Published --> Archived: Admin archives or user requests removal (approved)
Published --> Flagged: User reports abuse / content violation detected

Flagged --> Archived: Admin removes after review
Flagged --> Published: Admin reviews & clears flag

Rejected --> Draft: User receives rejection reason, edits and resubmits

Archived --> [*]

note right of Draft
  Initial state after creation
  User can edit all fields
  Gallery photos are pending
end note

note right of PendingModeration
  Awaiting admin approval
  Cannot edit (except owner)
  Gallery photos are pending
end note

note right of Approved
  Admin has approved content
  Ready to be published
  Can still be edited or removed
end note

note right of Published
  Visible to all users
  Listed in search/map
  Cannot edit (removal request required)
end note

note right of Archived
  Out of public view
  Preserved in DB for audit
  Cannot be reverted
end note

note right of Flagged
  Marked for review
  Still visible during review (admin only)
  Can be reactivated if cleared
end note

@enduml
